Day 46 - 1123*
The story was really good. It didn't waste too many panels in doing the same step, while also letting us see he succeed in each part. I felt really good for him and that's a major plus. The art wasnt as good as the plot though so I can't go it a rating too high.
7/10.
the plots a bit too random but its noice
